      !  Subroutine   :                 ppm_ode_map_push
      !-------------------------------------------------------------------------
      !
      !  Purpose      : pushes whats needed of the buffer
      !
      !  Input        : odeid                   (I) mode to push
      !                 bfr(:,:)               (F) buffer to push
      !                 lda                    (I) leading dimension
      !                 Npart                  (I) number of particles
      !
      !  Output       : info                   (I) return status
      !
      !  Remarks      : 
      !
      !  References   : 
      !
